  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<p>Our escorted tours are a great way to see Italy with a group of like-minded travellers. Whether that’s discovering the fascinating history of Pompeii on our <a data-udi="umb://document/5b59497cc13d42cc9b7c342e57f46559" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b59497cc13d42cc9b7c342e57f46559}" title="Neapolitan Splendours Escorted Tour">Neapolitan Splendours tour</a>, heading to the little-know city of Matera on our <a data-udi="umb://document/bb217f2aad104295868ed1c2c8af3496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb217f2aad104295868ed1c2c8af3496}" title="Best of Puglia Escorted Tour">Best of Puglia &amp; Basilicata tour</a>, or trying some of <span>Sicily’s tastiest traditional dishes as you explore Palermo on our <a data-udi="umb://document/e633b3e5e57f4cd9bca1043e7c751e75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e633b3e5e57f4cd9bca1043e7c751e75}" title="Grand Tour of Sicily - Escorted Tour">Grand Tour of Sicily</a>.</span><br /><span><br />All our tours are exclusive to Inghams and have a maximum of 30 people. We’ve carefully planned each day to ensure you get to the most out of your trip, and the knowledge and passion of your guide will make it a holiday you’ll never forget.</span></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Have a look at our range of Escorted Tours below</strong></h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bb217f2aad104295868ed1c2c8af3496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb217f2aad104295868ed1c2c8af3496}" title="Best of Puglia &amp; Basilicata Escorted Tour">Best of Puglia &amp; Basilicata</a><a name="backtotop"></a><br /><br /></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/puglia/central-puglia/best-of-puglia-escorted-tour" title="Best of Puglia"><img src="/media/13072537/adobestock_87586758.jpeg" alt="Best of Puglia Escorted Tour" /></a><br />Tucked away in Italy’s ‘boot’, <a data-udi="umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd}" title="Puglia">Puglia</a> is known for its whitewashed coastlines and cyan blue waters. Visit the Trulli houses of Alberobello, the olive groves of Ostuni and vibrant town of Otranto in this UNESCO landscape.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bb217f2aad104295868ed1c2c8af3496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb217f2aad104295868ed1c2c8af3496}" title="Best of Puglia Escorted Tour"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/5b59497cc13d42cc9b7c342e57f46559" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b59497cc13d42cc9b7c342e57f46559}" title="Neapolitan Splendours Escorted Tour">Neapolitan Splendours</a><a name="backtotop"></a><br /><br /></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/neapolitan-riviera/sorrento/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour" title="Neapolitan Splendours"><img src="/media/13072514/shutterstock_759048709.jpg" alt="Neapolitan Splendours Escorted Tour" /></a><br /><br />Explore the dramatic terrain of the Neapolitan Coast with this fantastic escorted tour. From affluent <a data-udi="umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b38a4293ff04cc8b2dd360a57a538d8}" title="Sorrento">Sorrento</a> to glamorous Capri, the cultural and natural wonders of Campania are not to be missed.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/5b59497cc13d42cc9b7c342e57f46559" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b59497cc13d42cc9b7c342e57f46559}" title="Neapolitan Splendours Escorted Tour">Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e633b3e5e57f4cd9bca1043e7c751e75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e633b3e5e57f4cd9bca1043e7c751e75}" title="Grand Tour of Sicily - Escorted Tour">Grand Tour of Sicily</a><br /><br /></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/sicily/taormina-area/grand-tour-of-sicily-escorted-tour" title="Grand Tour of Sicily"><img src="/media/13072528/adobestock_34752426.jpeg" alt="Grand Tour of Sicily Escorted Tour" /></a><br /><br />This small group escorted tour will take you on a journey around the island, through <a data-udi="umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344}" title="Sicily">Sicily's</a> ancient towns, stunning archaeological sites and Europe’s largest volcano, Mount Etna.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a>Find out more &gt;</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
